	egins promptly at 8:30\n\n📩 RSVP: HERE \n\nFree to attend! Open to both Ch
	amber members and non-members. Don’t miss this opportunity to connect\, co
	llaborate\, and contribute to Kenmore’s thriving business community! \n\n\
	\#KenmoreBusiness \\#Networking \\#SmallBusiness \\#CommunityGrowth\n\nFro
	m SEAtoday - Community & Civic
