	 and outstanding works of art. Highlights from SAM's Collection tours take
	 place Saturdays and Sundays at 11:30 am Thursdays at 6 pm Monthly on Firs
	t Thursdays at 11:30 am and 1:30 pm This 60-minute tour meets at the top o
